name: Nasi Lawar Kambing
address: CCVP+Q2P, Jl. Kusanegara, Gunaksa, Kec. Dawan, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80761, Indonesia
review 1: We arrived at around 12pm and their menus are sold out. What's left is just the satay, soup, lawar. Everything is so good! Hopefully they add more quantities.
review 2:
I only remembered to take a picture as I had half of my foods. I love the foods especially gulai kambing. Perfect!!!
It is just that the place is too busy here. I would love to do take away in the future instead of dining in. The price is so affordable.
review 3: The best Mutton Satay and Lawar nearest Padangbai and Klungkung. You need to come before noon!
review 4:
This is my favorite place to eat "Nasi Lawar Kambing"
The satay and "Gulai" (goat curry) make it all so perfect
The Nasi Lawar Kambing Package just +-40k rupiahs
And its real made by lamb
review 5: I'm always so happy to have a meal here. Affordable price with great taste.

review 1: Must try! I've been there many times and still great!
review 2:

Just come and try this food.

review 2:
Best Balinese Goat Satay Meal on the island.
